This paper belongs to the field of natural language processing and conversational AI, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which specifically deals with natural language processing and generation. The paper also involves the use of neural architectures, which suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval and knowledge representation, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
